---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = '2026-03-31';
---
<Layout title="NudgeBit - Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for NudgeBit iOS app.">
  <div class="pt-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <a href="/en/apps/drift" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-accent-purple transition-colors">&larr; NudgeBit</a>

      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2 text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">NudgeBit - Gentle Habit Tracker</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-text-muted">
        <p>OpenClaw ("we", "us", "our") built NudgeBit as a free application. This page is used to inform users regarding our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Information Collection and Use</h2>
        <p>NudgeBit does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data to external servers. The app operates entirely on your device.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>No personal information is collected</li>
          <li>No usage analytics or tracking</li>
          <li>No third-party analytics services</li>
          <li>No advertising identifiers</li>
          <li>No account or registration required</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Data Storage</h2>
        <p>All habit data, momentum scores, and preferences are stored locally on your device. If you enable iCloud sync, your data is synced through your personal iCloud account, controlled by Apple's privacy policies. We do not have access to your iCloud data.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>NudgeBit does not use any third-party services that collect data. Optional iCloud sync is managed entirely by Apple.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>NudgeBit does not collect any personal information from anyone, including children under the age of 13.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:magic4e@gmail.com" class="text-accent-purple hover:underline">magic4e@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
